channel.title: Need help!Has anyone got TeamViewer?
channel.description:
SOLVED
Okay i got my Run.bat file to work by changed it to the correct type but still getting a few errors. But im having problems with my compiler it says: [code]The system cannot find the path specified. Press any key to continue...[/code] I have tried about 7different fixed and none have worked this is what is inside my compiler because i am on windows 7 x86. This is also a 508
[code]@echo off title compile cd ../src "C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jdk1.6.0_24\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/codeusa/Engine.java pause cls [/code]
Now my run.bat is okay but i need to solve these 2errors [code]Starting server on port: 43594 Error Loading banned hosts list Error loading banned users list[/code]
Inside the run [code]@echo off title Z508 cd ../build "C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin\java.exe" net/com/codeusa/Server 43594 pause cls[/code]
I am Running Java Version 1.6.0_24
Any help will be very happy by mean Thanks guys :)
